          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2123040671" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8663308115938441565">I was pleasantly surprised! I found this while browsing an online book shop. And I thought the summary sounded interesting, so I ordered it. <br/>Then I found the TV series based on this book starring Daniel Radcliffe and John Hamm. I saw the first season and enjoyed it so much. <br/>I stopped before continuing on with season 2, cause I wanted to read the book first.<br/>Next day I get my book order, I finish the book in 2 settings. And it&apos;s now one of my favorite books.<br/><br/>It was very short. And was more like a c</span>
  <span id="freeText8663308115938441565" style="display:none">I was pleasantly surprised! I found this while browsing an online book shop. And I thought the summary sounded interesting, so I ordered it. <br />Then I found the TV series based on this book starring Daniel Radcliffe and John Hamm. I saw the first season and enjoyed it so much. <br />I stopped before continuing on with season 2, cause I wanted to read the book first.<br />Next day I get my book order, I finish the book in 2 settings. And it's now one of my favorite books.<br /><br />It was very short. And was more like a collection of short stories. I think I enjoyed it a lot because I'm a young doctor myself and it just related to me so much. It was funny, witty, heartwarming and thought provoking all at the same time.<br /><br />Read this during the perfect time of my life. </span>
